                        <Text fx:id="chartReportC1Title" layoutX="17.0" layoutY="593.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Figure 1. Number of vaccine doses per 100 people administered over time in countries grouped by the GDP per capita. The number of doses plotted is the average of all countries in the quartile. All types of doses, including boosters, are counted individually. Hence, the number of doses per 100 people may exceed 100. " textAlignment="JUSTIFY" visible="false" wrappingWidth="466.9368591308594" />
